Package: scBridge
Type: Package
Title: Cross-Platform Single-Cell RNA-Seq Data Storage
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("scBridge", "Contributors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "noreply@example.com")
    )
Description: Simple, efficient package for saving and loading single-cell RNA-seq
    data in a format that works seamlessly with both R (Seurat/SingleCellExperiment)
    and Python (AnnData). Preserves all data components including expression matrices,
    metadata, embeddings, and graphs.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
